OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FA woman was shot by her father
OL,7,Ffollowing a "big" argument about
OL,8,FDonald Trump as she stayed at his home
OL,9,Fin the US, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FLucy Harrison, 23, had been staying
OL,12,Fwith her dad Kris Harrison and his
OL,13,Ffamily in Prosper, Texas, in January
OL,14,F2025 when she was killed.
OL,16,FThe fashion buyer from Warrington,
OL,17,FCheshire, had travelled there with her
OL,18,Fboyfriend Sam Littler for a holiday
OL,19,Fafter her dad moved when she was a
OL,20,Fchild, Cheshire Coroner's Court was
OL,21,Ftold.
