OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FGiving evidence Mr Littler said Lucy
OL,7,Fwould often become upset with her dad,
OL,8,Fwho the inquest heard had previously
OL,9,Fbeen to rehab for alcohol addiction,
OL,10,Fwhen he spoke about his ownership of a
OL,11,Fgun.
OL,13,FThe morning the couple were due to
OL,14,Freturn home to the UK, on 10 January,
OL,15,Fthere was a "big" argument between
OL,16,FLucy and her dad about Trump, who was
OL,17,Fdue to be inaugurated as president, Mr
OL,18,FLittler said.
