OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe said: "Kris and Lucy ended up
OL,7,Fhaving quite a big argument which led
OL,8,Fto Lucy running upstairs and being
OL,9,Fupset."
OL,11,FHe said Lucy had asked her father:
OL,12,F"How would you feel if I was the girl
OL,13,Fin that situation and I'd been
OL,14,Fsexually assaulted?"
OL,16,FMr Harrison had replied that he had
OL,17,Ftwo other daughters who lived with him
OL,18,Fso it would not upset him that much,
OL,19,FMr Littler said.
