OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe told the coroner's court that later
OL,7,Fthat day, about half an hour before
OL,8,Fthey were to leave to go to the
OL,9,Fairport, Lucy had been in the kitchen,
OL,10,Fwhen her father took her by the hand
OL,11,Fand led her into his ground floor
OL,12,Fbedroom.
OL,14,FAbout 15 seconds later he heard a loud
OL,15,Fbang and then heard Mr Harrison
OL,16,Fscreaming for his wife, Heather, he
OL,17,Fsaid.
