OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FMr Littler said: "I remember running
OL,7,Finto the room and Lucy was lying on
OL,8,Fthe floor near the entrance to the
OL,9,Fbathroom and Kris was just screaming,
OL,10,Fjust sort of nonsense."
OL,12,FMs Harrison's mother, Jane Coates,
OL,13,Fsaid her daughter, who worked for
OL,14,Ffashion brand Boohoo, was a "real
OL,15,Fforce of life".
OL,17,FShe said: "She cared. She was
OL,18,Fpassionate about things. She loved to
OL,19,Fhave debates about things that meant a
OL,20,Flot to her."
