OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FMr Harrison did not attend the hearing
OL,7,Fto give evidence.
OL,9,FAna Samuel, representing him, made an
OL,10,Fapplication at the start of the
OL,11,Fhearing for coroner Jacqueline
OL,12,FDevonish to recuse herself from the
OL,13,Fcase, saying a fair-minded observer
OL,14,Fmay conclude there was a real
OL,15,Fpossibility she was biased.
OL,17,FShe said the inquest had been
OL,18,Fconducted "in a manner more akin to a
OL,19,Fcriminal investigation than a fact-
OL,20,Ffinding inquiry".
