OL,3,CWoman shot by dad after arguing about
OL,4,CDonald Trump, inquest hears
OL,6,FLois Norris, representing Ms Coates,
OL,7,Fsaid the application was an "ambush by
OL,8,FMr Harrison's legal team".
OL,10,FShe said Mr Harrison was the "person
OL,11,Fin the room who shot Ms Harrison" and
OL,12,Fthe only person who was in the room
OL,13,Fwhen it happened.
OL,15,FMs Devonish refused the application to
OL,16,Frecuse herself.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
